#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="an10.110"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an10.110:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 10 "
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 10 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an10.110:0.2"
msgid "11. Samaṇasaññāvagga "
msgstr "11. Perceptions for Ascetics "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
#. VAR: 110. Niddhamanīyasutta → niddhamaniyasuttaṃ (bj)
msgctxt "an10.110:0.3"
msgid "110. Niddhamanīyasutta "
msgstr "110. Blown Away "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli5.221, sc1
msgctxt "an10.110:1.1"
msgid "“Dasayime, bhikkhave, niddhamanīyā dhammā. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, these ten qualities should be blown away. "

msgctxt "an10.110:1.2"
msgid "Katame dasa? "
msgstr "What ten? "

msgctxt "an10.110:1.3"
msgid "Sammādiṭṭhikassa, bhikkhave, micchādiṭṭhi niddhantā hoti; "
msgstr "For one of right view, wrong view is blown away. "

msgctxt "an10.110:1.4"
msgid "ye ca micchādiṭṭhipaccayā aneke pāpakā akusalā dhammā sambhavanti te cassa niddhantā honti; "
msgstr "And the many bad, unskillful qualities produced by wrong view are blown away. "

msgctxt "an10.110:1.5"
msgid "sammādiṭṭhipaccayā ca aneke kusalā dhammā bhāvanāpāripūriṃ gacchanti. "
msgstr "And because of right view, many skillful qualities are fully developed. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "an10.110:2.1"
msgid "Sammāsaṅkappassa, bhikkhave, micchāsaṅkappo niddhanto hoti … pe … "
msgstr "For one of right thought, wrong thought is blown away. … "

msgctxt "an10.110:2.2"
msgid "sammāvācassa bhikkhave, micchāvācā niddhantā hoti … "
msgstr "For one of right speech, wrong speech is blown away. … "

msgctxt "an10.110:2.3"
msgid "sammākammantassa, bhikkhave, micchākammanto niddhanto hoti … "
msgstr "For one of right action, wrong action is blown away. … "

msgctxt "an10.110:2.4"
msgid "sammāājīvassa, bhikkhave, micchāājīvo niddhanto hoti … "
msgstr "For one of right livelihood, wrong livelihood is blown away. … "

msgctxt "an10.110:2.5"
msgid "sammāvāyāmassa, bhikkhave, micchāvāyāmo niddhanto hoti … "
msgstr "For one of right effort, wrong effort is blown away. … "

msgctxt "an10.110:2.6"
msgid "sammāsatissa, bhikkhave, micchāsati niddhantā hoti … "
msgstr "For one of right mindfulness, wrong mindfulness is blown away. … "

msgctxt "an10.110:2.7"
msgid "sammāsamādhissa, bhikkhave, micchāsamādhi niddhanto hoti … "
msgstr "For one of right immersion, wrong immersion is blown away. … "

msgctxt "an10.110:2.8"
msgid "sammāñāṇissa, bhikkhave, micchāñāṇaṃ niddhantaṃ hoti …. "
msgstr "For one of right knowledge, wrong knowledge is blown away. … "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc3
msgctxt "an10.110:3.1"
msgid "Sammāvimuttissa, bhikkhave, micchāvimutti niddhantā hoti; "
msgstr "For one of right freedom, wrong freedom is blown away. "

msgctxt "an10.110:3.2"
msgid "ye ca micchāvimuttipaccayā aneke pāpakā akusalā dhammā sambhavanti te cassa niddhantā honti; "
msgstr "And the many bad, unskillful qualities produced by wrong freedom are blown away. "

msgctxt "an10.110:3.3"
msgid "sammāvimuttipaccayā ca aneke kusalā dhammā bhāvanāpāripūriṃ gacchanti. "
msgstr "And because of right freedom, many skillful qualities are fully developed. "

msgctxt "an10.110:3.4"
msgid "Ime kho, bhikkhave, dasa niddhamanīyā dhammā”ti. "
msgstr "These are the ten qualities that should be blown away.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an10.110:3.5"
msgid "Dasamaṃ. "
msgstr ""

